This folder includes all datasets and accompanying figure for the paper submitted to ISSI 2023

'A probabilistic model of ‘Hype’ in scientific abstracts'


File:

1 - issi_hype.csv : hype_term, pmid, abstract_percentile
                    e.g. major, 35, 0.028
                    
2 - hype_feature_percentile.csv: Hype_feature, pmid, abstract_percentile
                                e.g. strongly_result, 11523050, 0.891
                                
                                
                                
3 - issi_modelled_hype_terms: includes modelled figure for each hype term.
e.g. promising_model_issi.png
